This merge request adds the following features:
1. -c flag to stop after generating C code
2. -t flag to use stub functions
3. print() and println() while using -t

pr_body:
This PR adds
1. support for the modulo (%) operator
2. support for octal and hexadecimal integers
3. bitwise operators >> and << (left and right shifts) which work on integers
4. tests and updated documentation
